            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. <date>Temporibus domni nostri <rs key="#Personal_rank"
                                >viri precellentissimi</rs>
                            <persName ref="#people/2000" key="#Princeps">Grimoaldi</persName>, Dei
                            providencia, Beneventane provincie <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>,
                            mense septembris, VIIII. indiccione</date>. Ideoque ego <persName
                            ref="#people/1902">Alahis</persName>, filius bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Arichis">Arichis</name></persName>, benigno
                        desiderio, pro me redepmcione anime, per hanc meam <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">chartulam conscripcionis</rs>, offero in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1900" key="#Monasteries #Abbots">Beati
                            Vincencii</orgName>, ubi Deo favente, <persName ref="#people/2001"
                            key="#Abbots">Iosue</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preest, omnes <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >rebus</rs> substancie mee, que habeo in <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines #Landed_possessions" ref="#estates/1902"
                            >Benevento</geogName> et in <geogName key="#Fines #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#estates/1903">Salerno</geogName>; et rem meam quam habeo non longe
                        ab <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1902">Sancti
                            Medici</orgName>, ubi <placeName key="#Churches #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#places/2306">Forano</placeName> dicitur, vel que cetera nomina ibi
                        vocatur, queque michi ibi a singulis hominibus datum fuit; simulque et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">rem</rs> meam quam habeo in <rs key="#Fines"
                            >finibus</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines #Landed_possessions" ref="#estates/1906"
                            >Capue</geogName>, seu et in <geogName key="#Fines #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#estates/1904">Telesinis</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Fines #Landed_possessions" ref="#estates/1905">Alifanis</geogName>
                        <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>; simulque et <rs key="#Forests">silvam</rs>
                        meam, que vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Exceptive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#places/2307">Silva Nigra</placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra vacua</rs> in integrum, quam a parte
                        bone memorie domni <persName ref="#people/373">Grimoaldi</persName>
                        concessam habui; nec non et <rs key="#Mills">molinum</rs> meum in <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Mills #Oil" ref="#places/2305">Teonsa</placeName> in
                        integrum, cum <rs key="#Oil">oliveto</rs> quem a singulos homines comparatum
                        et cambiatum habui; quam et insimul in prefato cenobio optuli omnes <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour #Slave">servos et ancillas</rs> meas, cum cespitibus
                        et conquisitibus eorum; simulque et <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casas</rs> meas in civitatibus, tam in veteri Benevento quam et in
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fruits/vegetables" ref="#places/84">Salerno</placeName> cum <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">berzario</rs>; et intus hanc <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fruits/vegetables"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventum</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs>, tam de iuri parentum quam et quod ego emi,
                        quam et ipsam <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casam novam</rs> quam ego
                        condidi, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casam cum curte</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">berzario</rs>; quam eciam et omnia peculia mea,
                        tam <rs key="#Horses">caballos</rs> domitos et indomitos, <rs key="#Cows"
                            >iumenta, bacce</rs>, <rs key="#Pigs">porcos</rs>, <rs key="#Sheep"
                            >pecudes</rs>, <rs key="#Goats">capras</rs>; quam et insimul omnem rem
                        meam quicquid per diversa loca habeo vel habiturus fuero in iam dicto Sancti
                        Vincencii eveniant monasterio possidendum, sine heredum meorum vel
                        cuiuslibet requisicione. Et hanc cartulam eo tenore <persName key="#Notary"
                                ><name ref="Tundipertus">Tundipertum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> scribere rogavi.</ab>
